            "id": "b66543cf-11d4-48b1-9d14-7122f2268864",
            "type": "markdown",
            "properties": { "expanded": true },
            "content": "\n# 👋 Welcome to **Introduction to Grail and DQL – Part 2**\n\nIn this course, you will learn how to:\n\n- **Parse and transform complex log and metric data** using advanced DQL techniques  \n- **Use OpenPipeline** to pre‑process data before querying with DQL  \n- **Build DQL queries** that generate Dynatrace Copilot prompts for intelligent automation  \n- **Utilize the new Smartscape model** in DQL queries for topology‑aware observability  \n- **Customize the MCP server** to extend observability workflows using DQL  \n\n---\n\n## 🧪 Exercise Data Source\n\nAll hands‑on exercises use telemetry produced by the **OpenTelemetry Demo** running in a **Kubernetes** cluster. The demo is a polyglot microservices web store that emits logs, metrics, and traces via OTLP.\n\n---\n\n## 📚 Training Structure\n\nThis training section is made up of **6 parts**:\n\n1. **Advanced Parsing with DQL**  \n2. **Data Pre‑Processing using OpenPipeline**  \n3. **Copilot Integration through DQL Queries**  \n4. **Topology‑Aware Observability with Smartscape**  \n5. **Extending Workflows via MCP Server Customization**  \n6. **Hands‑on Exercises and Best Practices**  \n\n---\n\n## 🗺️ Service Architecture (Simplified)\n\n            +-------------------+\n            |   Load Generator  |\n            +---------+---------+\n                      |\n                      |  (HTTP Requests)\n                      v\n            +-------------------+\n            |     Frontend      |\n            +---------+---------+\n                      |\n                      |  (Routes Requests)\n                      v\n    +---------+-------+-------+---------+\n    | Catalog | Reviews | Ads | Cart    |\n    +----+----+----+----+-----+----+----+\n         |         |        |       |\n         |         |        |       |  (Service Calls)\n         v         v        v       v\n    +---------+-------+-------+---------+\n    | Checkout | Payment | Shipping     |\n    +----+-----+----+----+--------------+\n         |          |          |\n         |          |          |  (Internal API Calls)\n         v          v          v\n    +---------+-------+-------+---------+\n    | Currency | Email | Image | Quote  |\n    +----+-----+-------+-------+--------+\n         |\n         |  (Data Updates / Notifications)\n         v\n    +--------------------+\n    | Accounting | Flagd |\n    +--------------------+\n\n\n🔗 **Learn more about the OpenTelemetry Demo architecture:**  \n[https://opentelemetry.io/docs/demo/architecture/](https://opentelemetry.io/docs/demo/architecture/)\n\n\n---\n\n🚀 Let’s dive in and unlock the full power of Grail and DQL!"
          },
          {
